name: Dreaming Of Battle
description:
From the 100 Days of Drawing Series //

This 2021 personal challenge started in early March. The goal, to produce a finished piece, everyday, for 100 days  // This is day 18 of that challenge // 

"Part of the myth of the girl woven of leaves. She lives now, dreaming of battle" 

Minted for #HENOSY celebration
